name: Edit tag_name for an existing tag

elements.name: As a user I create a new tag on on tag manage menu

steps.name: I set scenario "Tag_manage_edit_tag" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/tags/new/']"
I enter "Tag to edit" into input field having xpath "(//input[@id='tag-name'])[1]"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-blue"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/tags/tag-to-edit/']"
I enter "Tag to edit edited" into input field having xpath "(//input[@id='tag-name'])[1]"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-blue"
I should see text "Tag to edit edited"
